{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "15", "m": "03", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "08", "M": "24", "S": "08"}}, "news": [{"title": "Telangana government yet to set up municipal building tribunal despite HC directive in 2022", "para": "Despite a decade-old provision and a four-year-old assurance to the Telangana High Court, the state government has failed to establish the Municipal Building Tribunal (MBT). This delay exacerbates the mushrooming of unauthorized structures, leaving thousands of cases pending in courts. The tribunal, intended to streamline building-related disputes, remains elusive, impacting effective governance and legal recourse.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/telanganas-municipal-building-tribunal-still-not-established-despite-urgent-need/129568119?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-1967773/129568119.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Maharashtra government to set up new IT park near proposed Purandar airport", "para": "Maharashtra government announced a new IT park near the proposed international airport in Purandar. The move aims to attract IT companies by offering better infrastructure, potentially creating one lakh jobs. Experts urged the government to learn from Hinjewadi's past mistakes and ensure world-class amenities.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/maharashtra-announces-new-it-park-near-purandar-airport-to-boost-job-creation/129568070?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-187074/129568070.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "Kochi: After years-long wait, Bliss City project to become reality", "para": "Kochi Metro Rail Ltd's ambitious Bliss City project in Kakkanad is moving forward with the leasing of its first land parcels. This 31.43-acre mixed-use development, a collaboration with NBCC, will feature commercial, shopping, and entertainment facilities, including a proposed theme park and I-Max theatre, aiming to become a premier business and leisure destination.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/kochis-bliss-city-project-a-new-era-of-development-in-kakkanad/129567842?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-275884/129567842.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}